{"id": "1417915730187518144", "channel_id": "1417842352642588692", "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "content": "There are two posion teams endgame:\n\n1. 24 Blue. The unit 24 (you don't have) in Chaos with blue is one of the best teams in the endgame. \n\n2. Liz + Lily team. This team you can make right now. But it is one of the harder teams to learn how to play. It's often not recommended to beginners as it can be hard to play.\n\nLiz / Lily / Horla + 1 more unit will work for you.", "timestamp": "2025-09-17T16:50:53.677000+00:00", "thread_id": "1417842352642588692", "reactions": [{"emoji": "💗", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}]}
{"id": "1417916942718730440", "channel_id": "1417842352642588692", "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "content": "As for who to select in standard, the best options are:\n\nJenkins (purple)\nWinkle (purple)\nCaecus (blue)\nFaint (red)\n\nAnd Nautila (yellow) but you have her.", "timestamp": "2025-09-17T16:55:42.767000+00:00", "thread_id": "1417842352642588692", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-17T16:56:06.382000+00:00"}
